India’s April-September Gross Direct Tax Collection Rises 23%

-- B y   P r a t i k   P a r i j a
-- 
2011-10-07T14:37:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/india-s-april-september-gross-direct-tax-collection-rises-23-.html
India ’s gross direct tax collection
for the six months ended September rose 23 percent to 2.57
trillion rupees, according to an e-mailed statement from the
ministry of finance today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
